txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Broken wood spears from the Orcs and shades north of Amon Raith. Deliver the items to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith.
'This calms me a little. Thank you.'
'William made mention that there are stronger Orcs and shades to the north. Will you help us out and get their broken weapons?'

You have accepted a task to deliver broken wood spears to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith in the North Downs. You can find broken wood spears from the Orcs and shades north of Amon Raith.
Wanted: Broken wood spears from the Orcs and shades north of Amon Raith.
